        <p style="color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">
         Happy Thursday!
        </p>
        <p style="color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">
         I\xe2\x80\x99ve been writing about web3 a lot. There are a bunch of reasons for that, but one of the main ones is that I\xe2\x80\x99m just a business model nerd, and new tools create opportunities for new business models. But I love digging into innovative and clever models wherever I find them, and today\xe2\x80\x99s focus,
         <a href="https://email.mg2.substack.com/c/eJxFUMuOwyAQ-5pyjHi29MBhL_sbiMckRZtABMNG-fulzWGl0Yw0lm3ZwSEspZ5mLw3Je1k8dzAZjrYCIlTSG1SbomF3roWSTxKNjEwrTVKzcwXYXFoN1g5k735NwWEq-cOglCvyMiJILYQSIVIeHnMI8hGUEpRGQbWPj8vX9ZggBzDwC_UsGchqXoh7u4mvG_8ecxzH1LLb9zqFso0HSYZTPoZRNvSFmPhEvZIzOD-zp9Yh-gnms7t47zdJt4VPrfuGLvy8JUg1uaAvNeVlwD8vt8H6AUYSO-7Wc8LTQnZ-hXiFxKurT2y7QIY6OozW4WhISkUZ5-zJxBVqtCC1olQISYZzLIOV_03_AM_5gQc" rel="" style="color: #1a1a1a; text-decoration: underline;">
          Snappr
         </a>
         , is a perfect example.
        </p>
        <p style="color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">
         It started as an on-demand self-service marketplace for professional photography, and by listening to its clients, it\xe2\x80\x99s built an enterprise SaaS and API offering uniquely enabled by the self-service business. It\xe2\x80\x99s a model and product roadmap that you probably couldn\xe2\x80\x99t have drawn up ahead of time, but that makes perfect sense looking backwards. And it\xe2\x80\x99s a case study in how to build an API-first business, last, once all of the right pieces are in place.
        </p>
        <p style="color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">
         Today\xe2\x80\x99s post is a Sponsored Deep Dive on a company that I invested in through Not Boring Capital. As always, I only write Sponsored Deep Dives on companies I would invest in, and in most cases, I actually have. You can read my
         <a href="https://email.mg2.substack.com/c/eJxFkctq5DAQRb_GWho93eqFFoEkDMlkNgMhWRk9qt2ibcmjxwT_feT2IlCqElXcuuLI6gJTTJtaYy5oT2PZVlABvvIMpUBCNUMavVNkoJIJfkZOcUekkMjn8ZIAFu1nVVIFtFYze6uLj-GuwJgKdFXE2LMeDLV2kFYSepKDw0YLLIlhAzsdvro6D8GCgv-QthgAzepaypo79tDR5xYu2txPMU4z9DYuR6cuEMp-bYe8Uu4eXsXt9PtX_XzLL2-bo9o-_v33Jc2Te1nG1fr3tLz_-dhXgvOlY881rx17zFedfJiQVxTTFgQTJhhjPe2xEfwC2lzIWUrrTA-XrWo31I7jZaJ9riYXbW_7o1BSIRYT911tfLvqBeb7oMEZW11q8GUbIWgzgzu4lQP_neQ4QYDUvsWNujTonAtMKCVnwg5ODSyXAmPGOGrOLjZV-DH9BgkMnLI" rel="" style="color: #1a1a1a; text-decoration: underline;">
          thought process on deep dives here
         </a>
         . I\xe2\x80\x99ll always disclose my conflicts. No conflict, no interest.
        </p>
