        <p style="color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">
         It was a jarring experience, partially because it\xe2\x80\x99s such an uncommon one at this point. Today, practically everything that consumers spend money on is mediated through an online platform with full price transparency. We complain about Airbnb\xe2\x80\x99s cleaning fees or DoorDash\xe2\x80\x99s delivery fees, but we know about them before hitting the buy button. Price transparency is table stakes.
        </p>
        <p style="color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">
         So last July, I was in the right state of mind when
         <a href="https://email.mg2.substack.com/c/eJxFUMuOhDAM-5rpEfXJlEMPe9nfQH0EplpoUZsu4u-3MxxWshIplmPZ3iKsuVzmyBXJe8x4HWASnHUDRCikVShzDIaNXAslJxKMDEwrTWKdlwKw27gZLA3I0dwWvcWY00dBKVfkZQLo8Sksk9Tp5-S59XSkdtR-AgUjl7evbSFC8mDgF8qVE5DNvBCP-hBfD_7dcZ7n4GyNtQIOPu_9RKLhlHcwyoQSQgx8oE7JBaxb2KS1D26A5Wo2jO0h6b7yoTZX0fqf9wtSTMrocolp7fTPy-6wfYieZe57byniNUOyboNwx8S7rU_weYUEpbcYZou9IykVZZyziYk7Vu9BakWpEJJ055C7Kv2b_gH-24Hh" rel="" style="color: #1a1a1a; text-decoration: underline;">
          Basis Set
         </a>
         \xe2\x80\x99s
         <a href="https://email.mg2.substack.com/c/eJxFUMtuxCAM_JrlGPFMkwOHXvobEQGToE0gAtNt-vUlm0Mly5Y1Go9nrEFYUj71kQqSq014HqAjvMoGiJBJLZCn4DTr-SCUHInT0rFBDSSUyWeA3YRNY65AjjpvwRoMKb4ZlHJFVm2Vl95Z8FyM0tKPnsM4cuWk8OPgXH_rmuoCRAsaviGfKQLZ9Ip4lIf4fPCvVvgK10edTXvbfir8riaRoDnlrRhlQgkhOt7RWUkPZvZsHAbr5g78WY3r60PSfeFdqXNBY5_XJZJ1TDinHOLS4OdqdtjeQHMztbnXGPCcIJp5A3cbxTuvt_VpgQi55egmgy0lKRVlnLORidtYS0IOilIhJGnKLjVW_Bf9A-Ftg30" rel="" style="color: #1a1a1a; text-decoration: underline;">
          Lan Xuezhao
         </a>
         , a Not Boring Capital LP, asked me if I wanted to meet
         <a href="https://email.mg2.substack.com/c/eJxFUMtuxCAM_JrlGPHMkgOHXvobEQQnQSUQgekqf192c6g0smVZ4_HMYhG2XC5z5orkXWa8TjAJXjUCIhTSKpQ5eMNGroWSE_FGeqaVJqHOawE4bIgGSwNyNhfDYjHk9GFQyhXZjRCMrxOdPIx0st6x1TE-Kj09R1ifmt26tvkAaQEDv1CunIBEsyOe9SG-Hvy7A1_h_dGw5KNPh6_LHmLsLwbDKe9glAklhBj4QJ2SK1i3sknrxbsB1qtZP7aHpMfGh9pcRbv8vI-RYlJGl0tIW1__7PaA-Fl0Q3PvR0sBrxmSdRH87RXvyD7u5w0SlB6lny32oKRUlHHOJiZubz0MqRWlQkjSlX3urPQv-gfanYQE" rel="" style="color: #1a1a1a; text-decoration: underline;">
          Matt Schiller
         </a>
         , the CEO of one of the fastest-growing and most fascinating businesses in her portfolio:
         <strong>
          <a href="https://email.mg2.substack.com/c/eJxFUMuOwyAQ-5pyjHi29MBhL_sbiMckRZtABMNG-fulzWGl0Yw0lm3ZwSEspZ5mLw3Je1k8dzAZjrYCIlTSG1SbomF3roWSTxKNjEwrTVKzcwXYXFoN1g5k735NwWEq-cOglCvyMiJILYQSIVIeHnMI8hGUEpRGQbWPj8vX9ZggBzDwC_UsGchqXoh7u4mvG_8ecxzH1LLb9zqFso0HSYZTPoZRNvSFmPhEvZIzOD-zp9Yh-gnms7t47zdJt4VPrfuGLvy8JUg1uaAvNeVlwD8vt8H6AUYSO-7Wc8LTQnZ-hXiFxKurT2y7QIY6OozW4WhISkUZ5-zJxBVqtCC1olQISYZzLIOV_03_AM_5gQc" rel="" style="color: #1a1a1a; text-decoration: underline;">
           Snappr
          </a>
         </strong>
         .
        </p>
        <p style="color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">
         <strong>
          Snappr
         </strong>
         started its life in the US in 2017 as a B2C photography marketplace. I don\xe2\x80\x99t know how I missed them when I was doing my photographer search, but it was exactly what I\xe2\x80\x99d needed. I mean, check this out:
        </p>
