        <p style="color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">
         And Workflows is a game changer for Snappr\xe2\x80\x99s business. It turns the product from on-demand to API-first, like a Zapier for the visual content pipeline.
         <strong>
          Snappr\xe2\x80\x99s story is an accidental playbook for building an API-first business, backwards.
         </strong>
         So today, we\xe2\x80\x99ll dive into the evolution by covering:
        </p>
