        <p style="color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">
         At that point, what the B2C product would become was actually pretty clear. In the February 2017
         <a href="https://email.mg2.substack.com/c/eJxFUcmu3CAQ_JrhhsXmefjAIZf8hsXSttHYgFgS-e_TM3OI1KpGlJoqqr3tsOd6m5JbJ29Y-13AJPjbTugdKhkN6hqD4U-h5awWEowKXM-axLZuFeCy8TS9DiBluDN622NOnwnGxEwOE4TjQTsVfpydn8uT-8ULvTkphHLM6q-uHSFC8mDgD9Q7JyCnOXov7SF_PcRvrA7-8HUkf0w-X3ghGP_BxgQClwgt2VIqvewLGo2d2m3LNVh3Au2Z4hEqtbTUvEFr6NKetBy5573aciCXEw34nxTwLRKNYAKLMy5nKeUkJuZmtYF1G1-09sFNsN3Dhud4KHbtYmrDtW796-2PVJNyd7nGtCP9OuwF54fAmFbs10ix3yukt7_wTbB_F_HJdN0hQcUFhdV2jF-pmXEh-MLlNzGMWOmZMSkVQeWQcSr9F_0HhmChiA" rel="" style="color: #1a1a1a; text-decoration: underline;">
          TechCrunch article
         </a>
         announcing Snappr\xe2\x80\x99s YC acceptance, they laid out the customer value prop that has remained central to the
         <strong>
          Shoots
         </strong>
         product today: on-demand, affordable, high-quality, and transparent.
        </p>
        <div style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px;">
